          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Can you reposition an existing brand?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, but it requires consistent messaging across every touchpoint for 6-12 months minimum before market awareness shifts. Repositioning is expensive: budget for a full identity refresh, messaging rewrite, and customer-communication programme in parallel.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
